      <Placemark>
        <name>AI Council Assessment</name>
        <styleUrl>#intel</styleUrl>
        <description>The U.S. military is increasing its presence in the region around Iran, including testing new stealthy equipment and expanding food modernization efforts for troops. There are also ongoing peace talks between the United States and Iran facilitated by Pakistan, with concerns raised about potential civilian casualties.</description>
